<p>
  On the internet, I go by <b>Vivelin</b>. I am passionate about video games<a href="#steam"><sup>[1]</sup></a><a href="#ffxiv"><sup>[2]</sup></a>, music<a href="#lastfm"><sup>[3]</sup></a><a href="#bandcamp"><sup>[4]</sup></a>, and
