</p>
<p>
  One of my recent projects is a more casual, accessible version of the
  <a href="https://samus.link/" target="_blank">Super Metroid & A Link to the Past crossover randomizer</a>.
  It combines the <abbr title="Super Nintendo Entertainment System">SNES</abbr>
  games <i>Super Metroid</i> and <i>The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past</i>
  into a single game, and shuffles the items between both games.
</p>
<p>
  <a asp-page="/Projects/SMZ3">My version of it</a> makes it more casual and
  approachable. It is a Windows desktop app, which allows for better
  integration and enables features such as a built-in voice-enabled item
  tracker. Several community members have contributed custom sprite work as
  well as some features that were not accepted into the original version.
</p>

